Program: Free Thinking
Title: Westerns, The Oscars
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b06v2k6c
Last Broadcast Date: Thu 14 Jan 2016
Matthew Sweet is joined by Professor Christopher Frayling to look at the revival of Westerns and Briony Hanson and Laurence Scott consider the 2016 Oscar contenders. Quentin Tarrantino's The Hateful Eight is out in cinemas now certificate 18. Alejandro González Iñárritu's The Revenant opens in cinemas in the UK on Friday January 15th Certificate 15. Show less